## The Reporting Calendar

All scheduled reporting is added to the ISSO's monitoring calendar — the same calendar that drives the M-1 and M-2 assessment activities:

| Report | Frequency | Due Date | Audience |
|---|---|---|---|
| Monthly monitoring summary | Monthly | 5th business day of each month | Health IT Manager |
| Privacy incident summary | Monthly | 5th business day of each month | Compliance Officer |
| Quarterly POA&M status report | Quarterly | 15th business day after quarter-end | AO (Executive Director) |
| Annual continuous monitoring summary | Annually | [Authorization date + 1 year] | AO (Executive Director) |
| Immediate notification (material events) | As needed | Within 24 hours | AO per Condition 3 |

